lead_paragraph: Wayne Rooney surpassed Ruud van Nistelrooy as Manchester United's all-time top scorer in European competitions on Thursday, leading the English club to a 4-0 win over Feyenoord and keeping it alive in the Europa League.

headline.print_headline: Rooney Leads Man United to 4-0 Win With Record-Breaking Goal
headline.main: Rooney Leads Man United to 4-0 Win With Record-Breaking Goal
